<br>
My final and permanent fix was to trash Windog98 for Windows 2000. Everquest runs faster, much faster and the crash issue went away.<br>
<br>
Also, I am running a GeForce3 card made by Visiontek and am using the latest drivers and this driver is fantastic. It solved a couple minor issues with text at high resolution and enhanced performance at max rez to boot. To top it off, the sound card is a SB Live platinum with the latest drivers.<br>
<br>
So far, the only complaint that I have is the incredible amount of time it takes to zone. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvesthewolvesden.showPrevMessage?topicID=381.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvesthewolvesden.showNextMessage?topicID=381.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvesthewolvesden.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=381.topic&index=13><img src=http://www.mr-bandwidth.com/aegiswolves/images/buttons/addreplybtn2.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvesthewolvesden.emailToFriend?topicID=381.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvesthewolvesden.threadControl?topicID=381.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvesthewolvesden.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=381.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvesthewolvesden.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=381.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub7.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="aegiswolvesthewolvesden">The Wolves Den<option value="aegiswolvesfrm11">New Worlds<option value="aegiswolvesfrm13">Track Scents<option value="ae